		<p>Confirma a exclusão deste Fornecedor?</p>
	</div>
	
	<div class="container">
    
	<div id="effect" style="padding: 0 .7em;"
		 class="ui-state-highlight ui-corner-all">
		<p>
			<span style="float: left; margin-right: .3em;"
